==English==
===Proper noun===
'''Persia'''

#The Western name of the [[country]] of [[Iran]] until 1935 was officially called "[[Persia]]". The native name of the country since Sassanian period is "[[Iran]]". Since 1935 both terms "Iran" and "Persia" are using in English. The [[w:Persia|Persian Empire]] once included most of Western and [[Central Asia]] and [[Northern Africa]].

